comment: Harden (HOU) takes an unnatural path and initiates the contact with Davis (NOP) prior to falling to the floor.
Holiday (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Holiday (NOP) that affects his RSBQ.
Beverley (HOU) makes incidental contact with Davis (NOP) as he deflects the pass.
Beverley (HOU) makes contact with Anderson's (NOP) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Brewer (HOU) sets the screen on Holiday (NOP) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Anderson (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position and does not affect Harden's (HOU) RSBQ.
Harden (HOU) cleanly strips the ball from Holiday (NOP).
Ariza (HOU) briefly engages with Anderson (NOP) and does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Holiday (NOP) makes contact with Harden (HOU) as he reaches in for the steal.
Beverley (HOU) makes contact with the ball after it has rolled off the cylinder and is no longer using the rim as its base.
Beverley (HOU) and Davis (NOP) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding. As the two players fall to the floor, Brewer (HOU) cleanly strips the ball from Davis.
Gordon (NOP) commits a take foul on Brewer (HOU).
